snippet.title: Taisei Project v1.3.1 — ReimuA Stage 1 Hard
snippet.description:
A gameplay demo of Taisei Project version 1.3.1, a free and open-source cross-platform Touhou fangame with an original engine.

For more information, visit https://taisei-project.org/
GitHub: https://github.com/taisei-project/taisei
Discord: https://taisei-project.org/discord
